64
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:27,620
Where's Lifei?

65
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,100
Oh, no.

66
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:30,500
We can't stop it.

67
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:06,610
This time,

68
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:10,850
