253
00:22:40,230 --> 00:22:40,770
Fine.

254
00:22:41,550 --> 00:22:42,290
Stay alert.

255
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:43,860
Don't push yourself

256
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:44,900
